name: Gina Kolt
description:
I’m considered as an attractive person and I’m new to this internet stuff as well.Much like me i would like to meet someone who is Honest,caring, financially stable and someone who have the capacity to laugh easily.I love going to the beach and i like hanging around but i will like to do that with my soul mate,Are you Compatible?? and i believe at my age i don’t need to mess around am a good christian and am looking for serious relationship to start new life with.I also believe Chemistry is important and and honestly,
I like intellectually who are bright but are not arrogant enough to want to tell the world how bright they are. I love stimulating conversation about deep feelings and everyday life. I am a little picky and generally know on a first or second date date if there is a match and will try to be honest and say so. I like people who make an effort to talk but am most comfortable around those who, I feel good to be with even when there is nothing to say. (if that makes sense) I am easy to get to know and try to make people comfortable with me immediately. Contact me, I think you are in for a slightly different experience.. and a laugh or two along the way.
